{
  "info": {
    "name": "SPOT Backend",
    "description": "SPOT 백엔드 API 컬렉션.\n\n사용법:\n1. 컬렉션 변수 baseUrl 확인 (로컬: http://localhost:8080, 배포: https://spot-study-pot-api.onrender.com)\n2. 'Auth > dev token' 먼저 실행 → 응답의 token이 컬렉션 변수 {{token}} 에 자동 저장됨 (이후 모든 요청에 Bearer 자동 적용)\n3. 다른 사용자로 테스트하려면 컬렉션 변수 userKey 를 바꾸고 dev token 다시 실행\n4. Group > create 실행 시 inviteCode/groupId 자동 저장, Join Requests > list 실행 시 memberId 자동 저장, Sessions > start 실행 시 sessionId 자동 저장\n\n주의: dev token API는 백엔드가 dev 프로파일일 때만 동작 (SPRING_PROFILES_ACTIVE=dev).",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }]
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8080" },
    { "key": "userKey", "value": "minji" },
    { "key": "nickname", "value": "Minji" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "userId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "groupId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "inviteCode", "value": "" },
    { "key": "memberId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "sessionId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "startedAt", "value": "" },
    { "key": "endedAt", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "request": {
        "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [],
        "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/health", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["health"] }
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "dev token (dev 프로파일 전용)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "var res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res && res.data && res.data.token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', res.data.token);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('userId', res.data.userId);",
                  "  console.log('token saved for userId=' + res.data.userId);",
                  "}",
                  "pm.test('200 OK', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"key\": \"{{userKey}}\",\n  \"nickname\": \"{{nickname}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/dev/token", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth", "dev", "token"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "naver authorize url",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/naver/authorize-url", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth", "naver", "authorize-url"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "naver login (code 교환)",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"code\": \"네이버에서_받은_code\",\n  \"state\": \"authorize-url_응답의_state\"\n}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/naver", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth", "naver"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Me",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "get me",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/me", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["me"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "update default goal (>=60)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"goalMinutes\": 120\n}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/me/default-goal", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["me", "default-goal"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Group",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "create group",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "var res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res && res.data) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('groupId', res.data.groupId);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('inviteCode', res.data.inviteCode);",
                  "  console.log('inviteCode=' + res.data.inviteCode);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Smoke Study\"\n}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/groups", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["groups"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "my group",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/groups/me", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["groups", "me"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "join group (inviteCode)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"inviteCode\": \"{{inviteCode}}\"\n}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/groups/join", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["groups", "join"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "leave group (생성자는 successorUserId 지정)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"successorUserId\": null\n}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/groups/me/leave", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["groups", "me", "leave"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Join Requests (생성자)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "list pending",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "var res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res && res.data && res.data.length > 0) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('memberId', res.data[0].memberId);",
                  "  console.log('memberId=' + res.data[0].memberId);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/groups/me/join-requests", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["groups", "me", "join-requests"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "approve",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/groups/me/join-requests/{{memberId}}/approve", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["groups", "me", "join-requests", "{{memberId}}", "approve"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "reject",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/groups/me/join-requests/{{memberId}}/reject", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["groups", "me", "join-requests", "{{memberId}}", "reject"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Goals",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "get today goal",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/goals/today", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["goals", "today"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "set today goal (11:00 KST 이전, 가입 첫날은 마감 후 1회 허용, 0분 허용)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"goalMinutes\": 120\n}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/goals/today", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["goals", "today"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Sessions",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "start timer",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "var res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res && res.data) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('sessionId', res.data.sessionId);",
                  "  console.log('sessionId=' + res.data.sessionId);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"category\": \"Spring\"\n}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/sessions/start", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["sessions", "start"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "pause timer",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/sessions/{{sessionId}}/pause", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["sessions", "{{sessionId}}", "pause"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "resume timer",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/sessions/{{sessionId}}/resume", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["sessions", "{{sessionId}}", "resume"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "end timer",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/sessions/{{sessionId}}/end", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["sessions", "{{sessionId}}", "end"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "manual session (자동 시각 계산)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "var now = Date.now();",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('startedAt', new Date(now - 120*60000).toISOString());",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('endedAt', new Date(now - 30*60000).toISOString());"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"category\": \"Spring\",\n  \"startedAt\": \"{{startedAt}}\",\n  \"endedAt\": \"{{endedAt}}\"\n}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/sessions/manual", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["sessions", "manual"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "today sessions",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/sessions/today", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["sessions", "today"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "open session",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/sessions/open", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["sessions", "open"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "delete session (수정 불가, 삭제만 가능)",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/sessions/{{sessionId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["sessions", "{{sessionId}}"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Dashboard",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "group dashboard",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/groups/me/dashboard", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["groups", "me", "dashboard"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
